[To] Vresa Nohdiir

[NPC Internal] Need anything doing round here?
[NPC] Vresa: Hum yeah why not!
[NPC] Vresa: Some of the gladiators here are getting better than I am at combat and I need a new weapon.
[NPC] Vresa: Surely Harnquist can forge one for me.
[NPC] Vresa: Give me a minute, I will write some specifications .
[NPC Narrate] -Vresa writes a few notes down on a scrap of paper.-
